304
00:16:46,507 --> 00:16:50,719
He's probably never had a woman
strongly come on to him.

305
00:16:51,929 --> 00:16:55,473
It hasn't been triggered yet,
but he does have that switch.

306
00:16:55,558 --> 00:16:56,600
I guess you have it, too.

307
00:16:56,684 --> 00:16:58,894
-I have that switch?
-You do.

308
00:16:58,977 --> 00:17:01,772
