-Yes, after.

314
00:17:17,287 --> 00:17:19,915
You all finally see
some discrepancy, right?

315
00:17:19,998 --> 00:17:24,545
The exchange between
Hikaru and Tamosan was rather young.

316
00:17:24,628 --> 00:17:27,047
