and said what he needed to say.

330
00:18:12,217 --> 00:18:15,262
And Nacchan cried
and he wondered if she's okay.

331
00:18:15,345 --> 00:18:18,599
Handa, in his maturity,
realized something must be bothering her.

332
00:18:18,682 --> 00:18:20,809
It's not because of the fishing.

333
00:18:20,893 --> 00:18:23,228
-Yes, he understood that.
-Yes.

334
00:18:23,311 --> 00:18:27,816
