with some aspects of shared living.

366
00:20:08,250 --> 00:20:12,129
-She was bothered.
-But she said she had fun.

367
00:20:12,212 --> 00:20:14,006
It worked out.

368
00:20:14,089 --> 00:20:19,094
-Problem solved?
-She said it was solved.

369
00:20:19,177 --> 00:20:23,807
