00:27:08,837 --> 00:27:10,380
-He hasn't.
-No?

497
00:27:10,463 --> 00:27:13,967
He hasn't said anything,
so I have no idea how Hikaru feels.

498
00:27:15,010 --> 00:27:16,344
Yeah.

499
00:27:22,142 --> 00:27:23,727
I'm gonna go shower. See ya.

500
00:27:23,811 --> 00:27:26,229
-Good night.
-See ya, good night.

501
00:27:32,027 --> 00:27:35,322
It's been like this
between the two of us lately.

502
00:27:35,405 --> 00:27:36,990
No way.

503
00:27:37,074 --> 00:27:38,617
Really.

504
00:27:38,701 --> 00:27:40,452
Are you okay after what he said?

505
00:27:42,495 --> 00:27:45,833
There were at least two things
that would've bothered me.

506
00:27:45,916 --> 00:27:48,669
At least two.

507
00:27:49,628 --> 00:27:51,589
I don't think he likes me.

508
00:27:52,464 --> 00:27:54,508
-Why don't you just ask?
-I don't want to.

509
00:27:54,592 --> 00:27:55,676
Why?

510
00:27:56,510 --> 00:27:59,722
I don't want to think about it right now.

511
00:28:00,806 --> 00:28:02,265
None of it.

512
00:28:09,189 --> 00:28:11,108
What should be done, Tokui?

513
00:28:11,191 --> 00:28:15,195
If the two of them continue to fight...

514
00:28:15,278 --> 00:28:18,365
Misaki might say she's tired of it.

515
00:28:18,907 --> 00:28:22,369
Hikaru says the wrong things
when he's upset.

516
00:28:22,452 --> 00:28:25,372
That personality won't change easily.

517
00:28:25,455 --> 00:28:27,207
That's true.

518
00:28:27,290 --> 00:28:29,585
He's too sensitive.

519
00:28:30,418 --> 00:28:35,173
As for the co-ed baths,
he didn't need to say he didn't want to.

520
00:28:35,257 --> 00:28:36,299
That's right.

521
00:28:36,383 --> 00:28:40,971
Misaki is cute.
She should be more clever

522
00:28:41,054 --> 00:28:44,975
about directing him and making him
want to do things.

523
00:28:45,058 --> 00:28:48,020
I think someone older
would be better for Misaki.

524
00:28:48,103 --> 00:28:50,438
-She needs a 60-year-old.
-A 60-year-old?

525
00:28:51,106 --> 00:28:52,315
-That old?
-Yeah.

526
00:28:52,399 --> 00:28:54,151
-Otherwise...
-Retired?

527
00:28:54,234 --> 00:28:56,612
Both of them are immature.

528
00:28:56,695 --> 00:28:59,322
They fight over every little thing.

529
00:28:59,406 --> 00:29:01,366
So the two of them make a perfect balance

530
00:29:01,449 --> 00:29:05,538
to the love triangle between Natsumi,
Hansan and Hansan's girlfriend.

531
00:29:07,998 --> 00:29:10,959
-I want to see both.
-Me too.

532
00:29:11,043 --> 00:29:13,962
Yes, but what about
Arman's life philosophy?

533
00:29:14,046 --> 00:29:16,089
Arman's life philosophy?

534
00:29:16,173 --> 00:29:18,341
-He said it very clearly.
-Yes, he did.

535
00:29:18,425 --> 00:29:20,678
"I go with the flow
and ride the wave when it comes."

536
00:29:22,137 --> 00:29:24,765
"It's enough to have a family
waiting at home."

537
00:29:24,848 --> 00:29:29,853
Maybe he has something we've forgotten
growing up and living in Japan.

538
00:29:31,146 --> 00:29:34,482
-As someone who grew up in Hawaii.
-Hansan got that, too.

539
00:29:34,567 --> 00:29:39,029
That's why at the end
he said, "Yeah, it's nice."

540
00:29:39,112 --> 00:29:41,031
But I wonder if I could say nice.

541
00:29:42,407 --> 00:29:46,704
Oh, but it was a rather dramatic night.

542
00:29:46,787 --> 00:29:47,913
Wasn't it?

543
00:29:47,996 --> 00:29:50,373
All three girls cried.

544
00:29:50,457 --> 00:29:52,125
It was very emotional.

545
00:29:52,209 --> 00:29:53,460
But Arisa will be leaving.

546
00:29:53,544 --> 00:29:55,045
-Yes.
-The exhibit is over.

547
00:29:55,128 --> 00:29:56,547
She worked hard.

548
00:29:56,630 --> 00:29:58,381
Will a new member appear now?

549
00:30:08,183 --> 00:30:09,643
Hot!

550
00:30:18,026 --> 00:30:19,862
Thank you for your help.

551
00:30:22,698 --> 00:30:25,784
-Looks good.
-Lasagna for my gratitude.

552
00:30:25,868 --> 00:30:27,494
-Wow.
-Smells good.

553
00:30:27,578 --> 00:30:29,371
It looks delicious.

554
00:30:29,454 --> 00:30:31,957
Thank you, everyone,
for helping with my exhibit.

555
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:33,751
Of course!

556
00:30:33,834 --> 00:30:35,878
It helped me a lot.

557
00:30:35,961 --> 00:30:38,338
Ready? Bon appétit!

558
00:30:39,882 --> 00:30:41,634
Have some.

559
00:30:41,717 --> 00:30:43,552
Did you make this from powder?

560
00:30:44,595 --> 00:30:45,638
No.

561
00:30:45,721 --> 00:30:47,515
-What do you mean by powder?
-It's tasty.

562
00:30:47,598 --> 00:30:48,766
It's good.

563
00:30:49,558 --> 00:30:52,770
-I'm home.
-Welcome back.

564
00:30:52,853 --> 00:30:55,438
What's this?
It looks super good.

565
00:30:55,523 --> 00:30:58,567
It's my way of saying thank you
for helping me.

566
00:30:58,651 --> 00:31:00,235
Really?

567
00:31:00,318 --> 00:31:01,904
This isn't enough then.

568
00:31:02,655 --> 00:31:04,447
I knew you'd say that.

569
00:31:05,949 --> 00:31:08,702
I'm glad I got to see the exhibit.

570
00:31:08,786 --> 00:31:12,623
-You really came alive.
-It was really cool.

571
00:31:12,706 --> 00:31:15,125
I thought it was like
a grand gesture of departure.

572
00:31:19,547 --> 00:31:24,176
But you worked really hard
and made it happen.

573
00:31:24,259 --> 00:31:26,720
And I know you were busy,

574
00:31:26,804 --> 00:31:30,849
but seeing the final result
made me really understand.

575
00:31:33,351 --> 00:31:36,063
I've decided to leave.

576
00:31:37,230 --> 00:31:40,108
But every day has been fun.

577
00:31:40,192 --> 00:31:42,653
At times I wasn't sure
if coming here was a good idea,

578
00:31:42,736 --> 00:31:45,488
but right now I'm truly grateful.

579
00:31:45,989 --> 00:31:49,284
It's like I have another home.
I'm so happy.

580
00:31:50,452 --> 00:31:54,582
To be honest, I never thought
I'd not want to leave.

581
00:31:55,415 --> 00:31:58,794
I'm going to keep working hard
so you'll say that I'm doing my best.

582
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:02,422
I hope you guys work hard, too.

583
00:32:03,716 --> 00:32:05,092
Thank you.

584
00:32:15,477 --> 00:32:19,189
We all made this for you.

585
00:32:19,982 --> 00:32:22,150
-What's this?
-It's for you.

586
00:32:26,321 --> 00:32:28,365
I don't remember when we took these.

587
00:32:32,077 --> 00:32:34,037
It brings back memories.

588
00:32:34,121 --> 00:32:37,124
Arman, I can't read English!

589
00:32:46,509 --> 00:32:48,886
Will you read it, Arman?

590
00:32:56,018 --> 00:32:59,021
No, not in English!
In Japanese!

591
00:33:00,355 --> 00:33:03,984
"Thank you for all the great memories.

592
00:33:04,067 --> 00:33:08,446
Continue to pursue your dream.

593
00:33:09,406 --> 00:33:11,074
Good luck."

594
00:33:11,158 --> 00:33:12,576
Thank you.

595
00:33:16,038 --> 00:33:17,289
Thank you.

596
00:33:23,045 --> 00:33:25,506
-See you, Arisa.
-See you!

597
00:33:29,467 --> 00:33:30,928
Thank you.

598
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:33,764
Thank you.

599
00:33:35,390 --> 00:33:36,809
Good luck.

600
00:33:38,769 --> 00:33:41,063
-Bye, Arisa!
-Bye!

601
00:33:41,146 --> 00:33:42,480
-See you later!
-Good luck.

602
00:33:42,565 --> 00:33:43,982
-Bye!
-Bye!

603
00:33:49,029 --> 00:33:53,033
NAGOYA, AICHI

604
00:33:56,036 --> 00:33:58,455
-You've packed everything?
-Yeah.

605
00:33:58,539 --> 00:34:00,916
-Will you double-check for me later?
-Sure.

606
00:34:02,459 --> 00:34:04,127
You'll be okay in Tokyo?

607
00:34:04,211 --> 00:34:07,923
I didn't think I'd leave you so soon, Mom.

608
00:34:08,006 --> 00:34:09,132
Seriously.

609
00:34:09,925 --> 00:34:12,052
You can come home anytime.

610
00:34:12,135 --> 00:34:14,262
Yeah, I will.

611
00:34:15,138 --> 00:34:17,641
Will you be okay living with boys?

612
00:34:17,725 --> 00:34:19,434
I won't be okay.

613
00:34:20,435 --> 00:34:22,229
I wonder if you'll find someone you like.

614
00:34:22,312 --> 00:34:24,523
That would be nice.

615
00:34:24,607 --> 00:34:29,862
If I can grow in some way
or gain something there...

616
00:34:30,696 --> 00:34:33,198
-I think you will.
-I think so, too.

617
00:34:33,281 --> 00:34:36,118
And then if I can come home,
I'll be happy.

618
00:34:49,590 --> 00:34:51,550
-Be careful.
-Yeah.

619
00:34:51,634 --> 00:34:53,426
I'll go now.

620
00:34:53,511 --> 00:34:55,513
-Call me anytime.
-Yeah.

621
00:34:55,596 --> 00:34:57,515
Come home if you don't like it.

622
00:34:58,641 --> 00:35:00,851
-Bye. Be careful.
-Bye.

